MKS CORP June Sales Fall 41.16% (Table) : 3507 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-07-08T05:02:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-08/mks-corp-june-sales-fall-41-16-table-3507-tt.html
MKS CORP (3507)  said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 41.16% to NT$22,137,000 from NT$37,623,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales             22,137           37,623    
YOY%             -41.16%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            177,690          223,123    
YOY%             -20.36% 
=================================================================
 